messages.message: Hi team, I have this ticket EPD-4574 (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-4574) which I'm unable to close because "AI Runtime Version" jira field is not filled out. What do I populate for this one? The link in the description of the jira field https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/shared-utils/py-utils/module-type-utils/src/py/instabase/aihub_utils/constants.py#L587 is also invalid
for anything that isn't affected by AI run time, which i imagine is the case for your bug fix, u can just write "N/A"
